  <official_title>A Randomized, Double-blind, Placebo-controlled, Multiple Dose Study in Patients With Coronary Heart Disease (CHD) to Assess Safety, Tolerability, Pharmacokinetics and Pharmacodynamics of Subcutaneous Administration of APL180</official_title>
